item.title: CVE-2016-9600|2024-08-06T02:59:02.245Z -- jasper -- jasper
item.description: JasPer before version 2.0.10 is vulnerable to a null pointer dereference was found in the decoded creation of JPEG 2000 image files. A specially crafted file could cause an application using JasPer to crash.
